metadata.name: Non_homaN #01doragon
metadata.description:
A half-dragon, half-human girl. She has a complex about her horns, which were broken in an accident when she was small.
She does not like people to see her face, so she wears a hood when she goes out.
She likes animals and big, oversized clothes.

半竜半人の少女。小さい頃の事故で折れた角がコンプレックス。
顔を見られるのが好きではないので、外出時はフードを被っている。
動物とぶかぶかの大きな服が好き。
